title: Bobby Gifts Girlfriend A Cameo + Kane Brown Talks New Music And Quarantine Life + Amy Plays 'Tupac or Shakespeare?'
itunes:title: Bobby Gifts Girlfriend A Cameo + Kane Brown Talks New Music And Quarantine Life + Amy Plays 'Tupac or Shakespeare?'
description:
Bobby wanted to lift his girlfriend's spirits after a hard day so he bought her a Cameo from Brian Bosworth. Kane Brown joins us to talk about his new song 'Cool Again' and quarantine time with the family. Plus, it's William Shakespeare’s birthday so we play our 'Shakespeare or Tupac?' game!
